.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
The people have 5 different jobs:  lawyer, firefighter, scientist, doctor, musician
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, writing, hiking, singing, skydiving
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the lawyer is the person who likes red
2. the firefighter is the owner of the dog
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who likes green
4. the scientist is the person who's hobby is writing
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the old-gold-smoker is the owner of the snails
7. the kools-smoker is the person who likes yellow
8. the person who's hobby is hiking is in the middle
9. the doctor is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the person who's hobby is singing
13. the musician is the parliaments-smoker
14. the doctor is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Job	|   doctor	|    scientist	|     lawyer	|    firefighter	|    musician	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Hobby	|     skydiving	|      writing	|      hiking	| singing	|     cooking	|
| Cigar		|     kools	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| lucky-strike	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
